  "title": "ADMISSIONS EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Job Description</strong></h2><ul><li>Assist Sales Team for international student’s enrolment to achieve annual new student recruitment, including course consultation, contacting Agent to explain course details, processing student pass, verifying details completed in applications and entry requirements, monitoring course fees payment and ensuring student collects pass</li><li>Monitoring student’s profile and details in school management system</li><li>Ensure student contract is signed and fee protection insurance is purchased</li><li>Issuance of offer letter and student contract</li><li>Responsible for student pass application using ICA e-system</li><li>Ensure accuracy in student pass application and submit timely</li><li>Ensure accurate tracking of all student pass applications using ICA e-system</li><li>Liaise with ICA officer for rejected applications and appeals</li><li>Provide support and analysis as well as suggestions and solutions for rejected student</li><li>pass application</li><li>Ensure courses offered by the school and permitted by SSG are updated accordingly in ICA Solar+ System</li><li>Prepare and submit regular report to Head of Department - student pass monthly report, Agent recruitment report, Student’s highest qualification mapping report</li><li>Liaise with marketing and sales team on student matters</li><li>Organise orientation and graduation ceremonies</li></ul><p><br /></p><h2><strong>Job Requirements</strong></h2><p>1. Proactive</p><p>2. Detail oriented</p><p>3. Ability to work in groups</p><p>4. Customer Centric</p><p>5. Min 1 year of working experience in educational administration or any industry</p><p><br /></p><p>Fresh Graduates are welcomed to apply</p>",
